## Description
<p><img src='data:image/png;base64,'/></p>

<p>Cryptomatte is a tool created at Psyop that creates ID mattes automatically with support for motion blur, transparency, and depth of field, using organizational information already available at render time. This organizational information is usually names, object namespaces, and material names.</p>

<p>Open-Source License<br>
Cryptomatte is licensed using the BSD 3-clause license.</p>

<p>Compatibility<br>
Cryptomatte v1.4 works with Fusion v9.0.2-17.1.1+ and Resolve v15.1-17.1.1+.</p>
